  <item nodeId="node-599">
    <command xml:space="preserve">exit</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">The Intersection&#x000A;There is an Arcade to the west, a large Gas Station to the east and the Car in the Intersection.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-600"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-600">
    <command xml:space="preserve">w</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Arcade&#x000A;Inside this arcade you see a prize counter, some games, and a ball pit. You can use your money to play games and win tickets. The tickets can be used to get prizes at the prize counter. There are exits in all directions to the Intersection.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see a prize counter (in which are a spinning top, a slinky, a rattle, a mini soccer game and crayons), a skeeball machine, a basketball hoop, a water gun game, a punching machine and a ball pit here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-601"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-601">
    <command xml:space="preserve">take rattle</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You do not have enough tickets for the rattle.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-602"/>
    </children>
  </item>
