  <item nodeId="node-376">
    <command xml:space="preserve">e</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Convenience Store&#x000A;The cashier seems occupied with someone on the phone. The actual store only has one shelf of snacks. To the west is the Gas Station.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see a snack shelf (in which are a bag of potato chips, a candy bar, an orange soda and milk) here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
