  <item nodeId="node-521">
    <command xml:space="preserve">look</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Arcade&#x000A;Inside this arcade you see a prize counter, some games, and a ball pit. You can use your money to play games and win tickets. The tickets can be used to get prizes at the prize counter.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see a prize counter (in which are a spinning top, a slinky, a rattle, a mini soccer game and crayons), a skeeball machine, a basketball hoop, a water gun game, a punching machine and a ball pit here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-522"/>
    </children>
  </item>
