  <item nodeId="node-621">
    <command xml:space="preserve">x water gun game</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A classic carvnival game where you aim at the target with your water gun and try to make the lights go all the way up. The potential payout is 20 tickets.&#x000A;&#x000A;It costs $10 to play.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
