  <item nodeId="node-644">
    <command xml:space="preserve">look</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Arcade&#x000A;Inside this arcade you see a prize counter, some games, and a ball pit. You can use your money to play games and win tickets. The tickets can be used to get prizes at the prize counter. There are exits in all directions to the Intersection.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see a prize counter (in which are a spinning top, a slinky, a rattle, a mini soccer game and crayons), a skeeball machine, a basketball hoop, a water gun game, a punching machine and a ball pit here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-645"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-645">
    <command xml:space="preserve">x punching</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Test your strength with this machine. The potential payout is 15 tickets.&#x000A;&#x000A;It costs $5 to play.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-646"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-646">
    <command xml:space="preserve">x game</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">(the water gun game)&#x000A;A classic carvnival game where you aim at the target with your water gun and try to make the lights go all the way up. The potential payout is 20 tickets.&#x000A;&#x000A;It costs $10 to play.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-647"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-647">
    <command xml:space="preserve">x hoop</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You used to play basketball in school, maybe your skills will come back to you. The balls are slightly smaller than regular and deflated a bit. This potential payout is only up to 30 tickets but its really fun&#x000A;&#x000A;It costs $25 to play.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-648"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-648">
    <command xml:space="preserve">x skeeball</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A game of skill, potential to gain upwards of 100 tickets. You are not very skilled.&#x000A;&#x000A;It costs $20 to play.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-649"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-649">
    <command xml:space="preserve">play skeeball</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You put $20 into the machine.&#x000A;You now have $69.&#x000A;&#x000A;You got 31 tickets.&#x000A;You now have 78 tickets.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
